Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.25,0:00:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, isn't that something.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.42,0:00:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was wanderin' about\Non her own in the western seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.26,0:00:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell of a good job there, mates.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.05,0:00:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A merfolk child...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.14,0:00:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get a good price for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.56,0:00:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right then, let's get ready for the auction.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.94,0:00:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yessir!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.23,0:00:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.54,0:02:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pray forgive me, Ilwer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.67,0:02:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've burdened you greatly...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.96,0:02:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous.\NI'm just glad you're home safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.51,0:02:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think you'd make it back alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.30,0:02:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He just got lucky, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.80,0:02:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget him, though.\NI'm gonna need one more status plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.39,0:02:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.35,0:02:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're sure it was all right for me\Nto receive a gold top-rank status plate?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.74,0:02:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm-hm. Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.65,0:02:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.78,0:02:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You promised, Hajime-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.66,0:02:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.33,0:02:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You promised me that if I worked real hard,\Nyou'd show me all the touristy places in Fuhren!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.96,0:02:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hajime-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.43,0:03:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard this city was\Na great center of commerce,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.18,0:03:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it seems there is more to the city than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.64,0:03:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meh, no matter who might\Ncome after us, I'll kill 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.48,0:03:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter who, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.98,0:03:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. They could be a god for all I care.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.63,0:03:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our true enemy, God himself,\Nis powerful and wise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.26,0:03:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he is not invincible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.26,0:03:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there will come an age where he can\Nno longer continue with his dark machinations.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.93,0:03:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One day, there will come a being\Npossessing the ability to defeat him,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.32,0:03:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,dear Tio.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.90,0:04:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.32,0:04:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Live on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.08,0:04:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tio, you've come!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.34,0:04:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Elder.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.05,0:04:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt a strange thrumming in my chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.67,0:04:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has something happened out on the continent?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.97,0:04:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems God has summoned forth alien beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.26,0:04:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And many of them, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.77,0:04:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.31,0:04:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This anomaly will surely have\Ngreat effects upon our world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.02,0:04:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something within me tells me so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.53,0:04:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear leader, beloved brethren.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.58,0:04:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know not what awaits me,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.91,0:04:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,nor what may happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.42,0:05:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I feel as if everything is soon to change...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.30,0:05:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it feels {\i1}good{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.31,0:05:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When were you planning on waking up?\NWe're going shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.36,0:05:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's perfect weather for a date!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.95,0:05:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look where you're going,\Nor you'll trip and fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.12,0:05:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hajime-{\i1}san{\i0}, Hajime-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.50,0:05:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.88,0:05:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An aquarium?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.60,0:06:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dang, a monster that can talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.69,0:06:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its name is... Lehman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.65,0:06:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you can talk, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.45,0:06:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've never met, right?\NIntroduce yourself, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.20,0:06:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Hajime. What the hell are you, Lehman?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.95,0:06:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I asked you what a human was,\Nhow would you respond?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.84,0:06:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well, if I must answer, then I am me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.46,0:06:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No more, no less.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.01,0:06:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a question of my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.01,0:06:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it that you can sense\Nthe presence of monsters?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.01,0:06:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably because I've eaten monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.02,0:06:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, this fish is so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.86,0:06:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wow, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.78,0:06:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna make me cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.12,0:06:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The goings got so tough\Nthat you had to eat monsters...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.24,0:06:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite all that, you've turned out all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.29,0:07:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.79,0:07:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hajime-{\i1}san{\i0}, we're supposed to be on a date,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.00,0:07:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but all you're doing is talking\Nto this old man monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.71,0:07:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, I'm gettin' in the way of your date?\NSorry about that, Hajime, my boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.51,0:07:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leh-{\i1}san{\i0}, it's time for us to depart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.05,0:07:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One last question. Why are you even here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.52,0:07:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I was off on my own on a journey,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.64,0:07:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I ended up swimming\Ninto an underground current,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.40,0:07:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which brought me up to the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.36,0:07:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.44,0:07:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L... Leh-{\i1}san{\i0}, so, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.15,0:07:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wanna get outta here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.08,0:07:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, my dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.00,0:07:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't mention it, Leh-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.33,0:07:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, when I was brought in here,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.17,0:07:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember there being\Na little merfolk girl, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.63,0:07:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poor thing. Seemed like she\Nwas bein' bought and sold, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.51,0:07:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a huge gang of slavers in this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.60,0:08:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better watch out, 'specially you, cutie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.06,0:08:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be all right. I hope you will be, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.48,0:08:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you! Farewell!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.15,0:08:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yue, surely you're not happy about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.03,0:08:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean him and Shea?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.36,0:08:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. In recent days, it seems there have\Nbeen some developments between them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.58,0:08:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be happy to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.08,0:08:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You would be happy that another woman\Nis growing close to the man you love?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.54,0:08:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not just another woman. She's Shea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.84,0:08:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are pigging out.\NIs it really that good?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.64,0:08:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Oh, Hajime-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.76,0:08:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just wondering, were you\Nreally okay with having Tio-{\i1}san {\i0}join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.94,0:08:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Joining us? She just took advantage of\Nthe confusion back there and followed after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.15,0:08:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you not like her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.28,0:08:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Eh, she's not a bad person, just a pervert.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.37,0:08:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.53,0:09:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like her a lot, even though she's a pervert.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.54,0:09:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.13,0:09:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my Sense Presence caught on someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.30,0:09:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sensed someone?\NBut we're surrounded by people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.30,0:09:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sensed them from down below.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.60,0:09:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Below?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.14,0:09:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the sewers?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.47,0:09:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were really small and weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.52,0:09:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.85,0:09:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.31,0:09:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your change. Thank you kindly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.98,0:09:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At first, she was always clinging to Hajime,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.82,0:09:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and her ulterior motives were\Nobvious to the point of annoyance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.20,0:09:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But after knowing her for a bit,\NI understood something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.87,0:09:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.95,0:09:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She always gives everything her all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.50,0:09:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll work hard for the things\Nshe treasures, for the people she loves.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.13,0:09:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good or bad, she faces it head-on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.13,0:09:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shea likes me, too,\Njust as much as she likes Hajime.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.88,0:10:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't like me in the same way,\Nbut she likes me the same amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.93,0:10:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't she cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.58,0:10:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hajime-{\i1}san{\i0}, is she...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.54,0:10:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.79,0:10:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! She got away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.58,0:10:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.25,0:10:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how much she'll sell for?!\NGo find her, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.80,0:10:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.26,0:10:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's one of the merfolk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.60,0:10:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They live all the way in the western seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.81,0:10:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is one all the way out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.15,0:10:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And because they're\Nso beneficial to the kingdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.94,0:10:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they're the only race of\Nbeastmen that are protected.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.73,0:10:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's obvious something\Nbad's brought her here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.50,0:11:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.21,0:11:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Myu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.17,0:11:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Myu? I'm Hajime. That's Shea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.50,0:11:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.21,0:12:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yummy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.63,0:12:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.55,0:12:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All clean now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.82,0:12:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, Hajime-{\i1}san{\i0}, you're\Npretty good at taking care of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.20,0:12:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's this coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.87,0:12:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's talk about where to go from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.16,0:12:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to figure out\Nwhat we're doing with Myu-{\i1}chan{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.37,0:12:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.88,0:12:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go, miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.09,0:12:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so Shea needs both you and my master.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.09,0:12:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what of my master, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.35,0:12:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you not think she will\Nsteal his heart from you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.81,0:12:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must see how incredibly charming she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.02,0:12:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want Hajime to find\Nmore things he can treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.48,0:13:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm the only one who's special.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.78,0:13:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she thinks she can steal him,\Nthen she can very well try.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.03,0:13:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you could?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.83,0:13:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I certainly don't\Nwant to pick a fight with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.16,0:13:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as he continues\Nto abuse me, I am very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.25,0:13:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You pervert.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.92,0:13:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, you got separated\Nfrom your mother, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.09,0:13:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.92,0:13:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Must be that gang of slavers\NLeh-{\i1}san {\i0}was talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.38,0:13:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Must mean they're running some kind of\Nblack market auction or something to sell her off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.76,0:13:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Selling a little girl as a slave...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.68,0:13:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like there's a whole lot\Nof shitheads hiding out in this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.60,0:13:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what are we going to do with Myu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.23,0:13:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normal thing to do would be\Nto leave her with the city guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.44,0:13:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you're supposed\Nto do when you find a lost kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.74,0:13:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.74,0:13:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Myu's merfolk. I'm sure\Nthey'll take good care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.08,0:13:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it, Myu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.58,0:13:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna take you to\Nsome people who'll keep you safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.87,0:13:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll help you get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.17,0:14:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, big bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.46,0:14:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but this is where we part.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.71,0:14:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.76,0:14:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I know, but--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.59,0:14:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna be with you! I like you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.90,0:14:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.65,0:14:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you hate me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.48,0:15:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.61,0:15:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.45,0:15:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hajime-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.13,0:15:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want the merkid to die,\Nbring us the white-haired bunny girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.76,0:15:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hajime-{\i1}san{\i0}, I'm going to find her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.72,0:15:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.26,0:15:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're my enemies now, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.19,0:15:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a wonderful time this has been.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.24,0:15:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I sensed you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.75,0:16:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Yue-{\i1}san {\i0}and Tio-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.08,0:16:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.67,0:16:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could ask the same of you.\NThis is a bit much for a date, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.59,0:16:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, have you become\Nembroiled in some sort of trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.42,0:16:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We saved a little merfolk girl\Nfrom a bunch of slave traders,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.80,0:16:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they took her away again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.31,0:16:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is she now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.93,0:16:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't find anyone who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.44,0:16:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were just torturing the information\Nabout their hideout out of one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.02,0:16:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we figured we'd make\Nan example out of these guys
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and take out all the gangs\Ninvolved in this business!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.11,0:16:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you help us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.87,0:16:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems he's found\Nsomething else he finds important.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.46,0:16:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it is your wish, Master, I cannot deny it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.08,0:16:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.75,0:16:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's split into\Ntwo groups and search for Myu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.71,0:16:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go with Yue. Shea, you're with Tio.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.72,0:16:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the hell are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.18,0:17:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.46,0:17:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hell are you doing?! Go find 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.01,0:17:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yessir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.67,0:17:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to look very hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.01,0:17:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.89,0:17:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A trade that victimizes innocent children...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.47,0:17:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must admit, I'm rather perturbed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.02,0:17:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reflect on your wrongdoings in hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.12,0:18:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you hate me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.83,0:18:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, cry! Scream!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.50,0:18:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't do that,\Nthen put on a little show for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.75,0:18:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare give me trouble,\Nyou useless idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.59,0:18:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should be saying those\Nexact same words to you, asshole.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.68,0:18:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.89,0:18:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.74,0:18:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Myu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.87,0:18:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you always soaking\Nwet every time I find you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.58,0:18:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.84,0:19:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Myu, close your eyes for a sec, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.18,0:19:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.94,0:19:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can open them, Myu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.95,0:19:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! We're flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.36,0:19:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not really flying, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.62,0:19:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you're gonna get\Nto see some real nice fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.50,0:19:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fireworks?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.83,0:19:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ready? Say "boom"!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.58,0:19:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boom!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.21,0:19:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Surprised? Those are fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.84,0:19:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fireworks are scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.15,0:19:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something came out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.98,0:20:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we're gonna destroy their hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.80,0:20:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her name's Yue. She's my lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.06,0:20:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No fair. She's so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.44,0:20:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did such a good job, Myu. Good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.53,0:20:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? Did you do something\Nmean to Myu-{\i1}chan{\i0}, Hajime-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.33,0:20:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, you think I could bully her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.00,0:20:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to bully someone, bully me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.12,0:20:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut it, you perv.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.92,0:21:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's our pervert--I mean Tio.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.38,0:21:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much, big bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.22,0:21:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure. Look, could you\Nstop calling me "big bro"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.76,0:21:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just call me Hajime.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.43,0:21:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then you're Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.89,0:21:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, don't tell me, that's how merfolk say\N"big bro" or "Hajime" in their language?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.61,0:21:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope! Papa means Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.78,0:21:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why "Papa"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.28,0:21:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't have a Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.57,0:21:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So big bro can be my Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.57,0:21:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, can you not call me Papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.99,0:21:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I look older,\Nbut I'm still only 17!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.91,0:21:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.58,0:21:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, you can call me "big bro"!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.12,0:21:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't complain anymore,\Nso just stop calling me Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.67,0:21:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! You're my Papa, Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.59,0:21:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hajime, I want a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.72,0:21:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.76,0:21:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, I, too, am fully prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.01,0:21:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us engage in procreat--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.39,0:21:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save the jokes for when\Nyou're looking in the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.39,0:21:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you only admonishing me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.44,0:22:05.15,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"Good morning," "Good night,"\Nall those simple things
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.15,0:22:10.24,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,are so dreamlike and beloved to me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.24,0:22:14.95,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I finally met you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.95,0:22:21.59,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is so special, thank you again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.34,0:22:29.72,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think I'd be lonely all by myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.72,0:22:34.93,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,That is, until you found me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.93,0:22:40.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.52,0:22:45.94,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,That is, until I thought of a world without you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.94,0:22:52.78,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you believe it?\NI miss you, I'm so fond of you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.78,0:22:58.58,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, don't forget it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.58,0:23:03.67,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Shine bright like the first star in the night
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.67,0:23:09.47,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and stay closer to me than anyone else
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.47,0:23:14.85,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never let you go
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.85,0:23:20.35,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never let go of that hand
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.35,0:23:27.90,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay by my side and shine
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.95,0:23:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ARIFURETA: From Commonplace\Nto World's Strongest.